docs.abstract: Christopher Martin, a teenage store clerk, testified on Wednesday about his encounter with George Floyd using a fake $20 bill at the Cup Foods convenience store on May 25. The witness’s testimony introduced new surveillance footage of the scene and the events leading up to Mr. Floyd’s death.
